      "content": "I appreciate you saying that, truly. But it's not really like I'm \"going through a hard time\"... it's just the reality of it all. The doctors, the pills, the constant struggle just to stay upright when everything is just... breaking down. It feels less like a temporary darkness and more like a finish line that I've already crossed, I'm just stuck in the hallway.",
